      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GRAND PERFECTION (1) was quickly into stride and burnt early from out wide where she gave a sight, finishing second (22.26) and beaten 1.3 lengths over 395m at this track. Comes through a solid form race last start. Rates highly and will give a great sight. WEBLEC BLOSSOM (3) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing fourth (18.33) in a Grade 6 at Mt Gambier. Safe beginner who has drawn to advantage. Bold showing expected. TAKE THE STEPS (5) is having his first look at this track. Missed the frame last time when 4th and beaten 1.3 lengths (22.44) at Warrnambool. Strong form has emerged from his last run. Leading chance. VELARIS (7) has claims fresh from a recent placing in good time.",
